## 5. 120‑Day Execution Bands (High Level)

We plug the agentic scaffold into your 120‑day war plan like this:

- Days 0–30:
  - Middleman live with basic agents:
    - Middleman Router (simple heuristics).
    - Billing Clerk (logs → CSV, Stripe manual).
  - StreetCode sends all executions through Worker → Middleman.
- Days 30–60:
  - Stripe metering live.
  - Operator console (AetherDesk) v1 live.
  - Telemetry Analyst agent and basic policy enforcement online.
- Days 60–90:
  - Multi‑provider routing.
  - Lane Architect agent proposing new `tap919:` SKUs weekly based on real usage. [billingplatform](https://billingplatform.com/blog/usage-based-pricing-examples)
- Days 90–120:
  - Fully agentic revenue operations:
    - Agents propose pricing changes, bundles, and experiments.
    - Humans approve/deny in a simple change management interface.

Everything revolves around one loop: **Middleman data → agents propose → humans approve → system reconfigures live**.

